		<title>20Employment</title>
		<content>  We conducted a survey of the children
 in Costock School to find the         
 occupations of their parents and where
 they worked.                          
  We found that 44% of{fathers}worked  
 in Nottingham,20% worked in           
 Loughborough,and 16% worked within a  
 five mile radius of Costock.20% worked
 more than twelve miles away.          
  About 65% of{mothers}worked.They work
 locally within a five mile radius.    
  The most common occupations for      
 mothers are teaching and secretarial  
 work.                                 
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
